    The Player class contains a Player.name and Player.id (unused right now), a Map<KeyBinding, Action> for all the possible Player.executables it may do in response to pressed keys, a State that holds the rendered, animated Player.state of the Player, and all the Player.hitboxes and Player.hurtboxes produced by the Player.
